reviewText: As promise deliver on time works great, and  great price good quality Thanks

Si esperas ver un concierto, no te gustara este DVD. Es un vulgar doblage, (lipsinging). Las canciones no estan del todo mal, pero me molesta sobre manera que pormocionen este DVD como un concierto en vivo, cuando en realidad el tipo lo que esta es doblando.

Luis Enrique sounds even better now than he did when he was younger.  And his lyrics are so soulful.  The setting was so intimate and very enjoyable to watch, that I felt I was at my own personal concert.  I was so taken by this DVD, now I have to get the matching CD!  LOVE IT!

Excellent DVD! It's a private concert.  Sound quality is phenomenal!!  Worth every penny!

- Salsero, Lou
